  <brief_title>Rifaximin in Minimal Hepatic Encephalopathy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Rifaximin on Driving Performance, Psychometric Test Performance and Quality of Life in Cirrhotic Patients With Minimal Hepatic Encephalopathy: Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Trial.</official_title>
