  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether alteration of gut flora with rifaximin can&#xD;
      lead to improvement in driving performance, psychometric test performance, and quality of&#xD;
      life in patients with minimal hepatic encephalopathy (MHE) and cirrhosis in a randomized,&#xD;
      blinded, placebo-controlled trial.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
